snippet.title: Just Dance 2016 Official Song List - Part 1 [US]
snippet.description:
Introducing Just Dance 2016 with a brand new way to play! All you need is your smartphone and the free Just Dance Controller App to play Just Dance 2016 on WiiU, XboxOne, or PS4. No extra accessories or camera needed. More tracks coming soon!

Bust a move to your favorite tracks including:

• Uptown Funk by Mark Ronson ft. Bruno Mars
• Want to Want Me by Jason Derulo
• Hey Mama by David Guetta Ft. Nicki Minaj, Afrojack & Bebe 
        Rexha 
• All About That Bass by Meghan Trainor

AND MANY MORE! 

Try Just Dance 2016 for free this summer! Visit justdancegame.com/app for details. 

Just Dance 2016 will be available on October 20th, 2015 on Wii U, Wii, PS4, PS3, Xbox One and Xbox 360

Visit our Website: http://www.JustDanceGame.com 
Join us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/JustDanceGame
Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/JustDanceGame
